 data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996325" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709026996325"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Als ich diese Tasse zum ersten Mal sah</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1773670886871" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1773670886871"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ich hatte zunächst nichts Außergewöhnliches erwartet.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Eine neue Teetasse – schlicht, vielleicht schön gestaltet.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Doch beim ersten Einschenken passierte etwas Unerwartetes.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sobald das heiße Wasser die Keramik berührte, begann sich das Motiv zu verändern.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Was zuvor zurückhaltend wirkte, wurde plötzlich sichtbar:</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ein detailreiches Drachenmotiv erschien langsam auf der Oberfläche.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Kein greller Effekt.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Keine auffällige Spielerei.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Sondern ein ruhiger Moment, der jedes Mal aufs Neue überrascht.</span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770383474865" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1770383474865" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/66b43615-0c55-4dac-9ede-01f200190293/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Image%20102.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1713946259430" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1713946259430"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Beim Drehen der Tasse fällt sofort die Verarbeitung auf.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Das Gewicht der Keramik.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Die glatte Oberfläche.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Das angenehme Handgefühl.</span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tee ist damit nicht nur ein Getränk – sondern ein kurzer Moment der Pause.</span></font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770383533297" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1770383533297" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/1b917ca2-3512-406c-91c4-9539722e4a64/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Image%2089.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770370823513" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1770370823513" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Lernen Sie die Farbspiel-Teetasse kennen</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996416" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996416" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Die Idee hinter dieser Tasse ist einfach:</p><p><br></p><p>Heißes Wasser aktiviert ein wärmereaktives Design, das sich beim Einschenken sichtbar verändert.</p><p><br></p><p>Die Kombination aus Keramik und Farbwechsel-Effekt macht jede Tasse zu einem kleinen Erlebnis.</p><p><br></p><p>Nicht laut.</p><p>Nicht übertrieben.</p><p><br></p><p>Sondern ein Detail, das den Moment bewusster macht.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1719232820743" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1719232820743" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/3b01082f-4000-4093-9d92-ac6616e240b2/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Image%2085.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770371028370" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1770371028370" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Was den Moment besonders macht, ist die Art, wie sich das Motiv zeigt.</p><p>Der Farbwechsel geschieht nicht abrupt – er entfaltet sich langsam mit der Wärme des Getränks. Erst erscheinen feine Linien, dann wird das Bild immer klarer, bis das Motiv vollständig sichtbar ist. Viele beschreiben genau diesen Augenblick als den spannendsten Teil des ganzen Rituals.</p><p><br></p><p>Sobald der Tee langsam abkühlt, verändert sich die Oberfläche erneut. Das Motiv wird wieder dezenter und verschwindet nach und nach in der Keramik. Beim nächsten Einschenken beginnt der Effekt von vorne – ein kleiner Überraschungsmoment, der jeden Tee ein wenig besonderer macht.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770383589435" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1770383589435" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/f0d1912a-c68b-4a1e-91d2-41aa701273c5/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Image%2096.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1773671082175" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1773671082175" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Mehr als nur eine Tasse</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770383573943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1770383573943" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Neben dem Effekt überzeugt die Tasse auch durch ihr Design.</p><p><br></p><p>Die Keramik liegt angenehm in der Hand.</p><p>Das Gewicht wirkt hochwertig.</p><p>Die Oberfläche fühlt sich glatt und ruhig an.</p><p><br></p><p>Mit 150 ml Fassungsvermögen eignet sie sich besonders für:</p><p><br></p><p>Tee</p><p><br></p><p>Matcha</p><p><br></p><p>Kräuteraufgüsse</p><p><br></p><p>Um den Farbwechsel lange zu erhalten, wird Handwäsche empfohlen.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996375" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709026996375"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-stretch-lg="0" data-stretch-md="0" data-stretch-sm="0" data-stretch-xs="0"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://rtrk.gartenpfad.com/click" target="" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc="" data-scroll-speed-md="2000" data-scroll-speed-sm="2000" data-scroll-speed-xs="2000" aria-describedby="a11y-external-message"><span>Verfügbarkeit prüfen 👉</span></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1773671117825" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1773671117825" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Viele Nutzer berichten, dass der Effekt jedes Mal wieder überrascht.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1773670922934" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1773670922934"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Ein kleines Highlight im Alltag</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709275370894" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709275370894" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275370944" data-id="1709275370944" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275382266" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709275382266" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/86baa072-3b60-434b-87fc-681308d7ac76/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Rectangle%2018.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1000" height="1000" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275372314" data-id="1709275372314" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275378713" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709275378713" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p><p>Perfekte Größe für bewusste Tee-Momente. Ich nutze sie abends zum Abschalten – der Farbwechsel hat fast etwas Meditatives.</p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">— Julia M. – ., 69, Leipzig</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709275493729" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709275493729" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275370944" data-id="1709275370944" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275493852" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709275493852" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/36cebd07-9881-4c94-9f3f-4780b3d64ace/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Rectangle%2042.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1000" height="1000" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275372314" data-id="1709275372314" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275493781" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709275493781" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p><p>Ein echter Gesprächsstarter im Büro. Kollegen fragen jedes Mal nach, wenn ich Tee einschenke. Genau solche kleinen Details machen den Alltag besser.</p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">— Andreas R., 52, Stuttgart</span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709275498296" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709275498296" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275370944" data-id="1709275370944" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275498217" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709275498217" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/86491405-2cd9-4d12-a218-a214f953fc45/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Rectangle%2043.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1000" height="1000" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1709275372314" data-id="1709275372314" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709275498338" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709275498338" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</p><p>Ich liebe Design-Objekte, die man wirklich benutzt. Diese Tasse ist genau das: praktisch, hochwertig und jedes Mal ein kleines Erlebnis.</p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">— Katharina W., 61, Freiburg</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996385" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709026996385"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Die Farbspiel-Teetasse entdecken</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1722256683867" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1722256683867" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/ce567a47-9c65-4c94-8f90-e0ef963e1106/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Group%2097.webp" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1000" natural-height="600" width="1000" height="600" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1770372553778" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1770372553778" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p></p><div>Die Tasse ist derzeit online erhältlich.</div><div>Weitere Informationen zu Design und Varianten finden Interessierte auf der Produktseite.</div><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>